title: Decentralization at Its Finest: Fezoo Coin (FEZ) Early Buyers Excited by Governance Features, Drawing Comparisons to Solana (SOL) and Ethereum (ETH
description: The operational word with cryptos and much of blockchain technology is “decentralization”. Cryptos try to achieve peer-to-peer interactions without the centralization and lack of control that dominates web2.  The best projects embrace this decentralization and use it to improve various aspects of the digital experience.
